# 🔹 String Operations

---

## Concatenation

If

```text
x="ab"

y="cd"
```

Then

```text
xy="abcd"
```

---

## Reverse

If

```text
w="abc"
```

Then

```text
wᴿ="cba"
```

---

## Power of a String

If

```text
w="ab"
```

Then

```text
w²="abab"

w³="ababab"
```

